OL,3,CMP rejects criticism from 'armchair
OL,4,Cgenerals' over protest attendance
OL,6,FDUP MP Carla Lockhart has defended
OL,7,Fbeing pictured with masked protesters
OL,8,Fat a march in Scarva over the weekend.
OL,10,FMs Lockhart said it was a "very
OL,11,Fvolatile situation" and she was in
OL,12,FScarva with other unionist elected
OL,13,Frepresentatives to de-escalate
OL,14,Ftensions.
OL,16,FMs Lockhart told UTV: "We were able to
OL,17,Fcome, stand up, de-escalate, try and
OL,18,Fcalm tensions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781021473
OL,3,CMP rejects criticism from 'armchair
OL,4,Cgenerals' over protest attendance
OL,6,F"We have armchair generals sitting at
OL,7,Fhome, scrolling through Twitter,
OL,8,Fcommenting after an event takes place."
OL,10,FShe continued: "I am going to take no
OL,11,Flectures from anyone who was not here
OL,12,Fon the ground, dealing with what was a
OL,13,Fvery volatile situation.
OL,15,F"I don't want people to feel they have
OL,16,Fto wear masks.
OL,18,F"I want them to be able to stand up
OL,19,Ffor what they believe, and keep their
OL,20,Ffaces from being hidden.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781021473
OL,3,CMP rejects criticism from 'armchair
OL,4,Cgenerals' over protest attendance
OL,6,F"But we were dealing with a very
OL,7,Fvolatile situation."
OL,9,FDuring events, Ms Lockhart was
OL,10,Fphotographed standing near masked
OL,11,Findividuals in Scarva as the march
OL,12,Fpassed by.
OL,14,FSinn Fein MLA Colm Gildernew told the
OL,15,Fassembly on Monday that "attempts by
OL,16,Fthe DUP to deflect are pathetic".
OL,18,FHe continued: "People see through them
OL,19,Fand see them for what they are.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781021473
OL,3,CMP rejects criticism from 'armchair
OL,4,Cgenerals' over protest attendance
OL,6,F"Again, we see the DUP standing on the
OL,7,Fwrong side, determined to drag us all
OL,8,Fback to the past rather than looking
OL,9,Fforward."
OL,11,FSpeaking at Stormont on Monday, DUP
OL,12,Fleader Gavin Robinson said it was
OL,13,F"entirely appropriate" Ms Lockhart,
OL,14,Falong with MLAs Jonathan Buckley and
OL,15,FDiane Forsythe, were there.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@VO]
