OL,3,CMP rejects criticism from 'armchair
OL,4,Cgenerals' over protest attendance
OL,6,FHundreds turned out in Scarva on
OL,7,FSaturday in opposition to the Great
OL,8,FMarch for Gaza, organised by the
OL,9,FIreland-Palestine Solidarity Campaign
OL,10,F(IPSC), which was due to pass by on
OL,11,Fthe Newry towpath en route from Lurgan
OL,12,Fto Newry.
OL,14,FThere was a heavy police presence
OL,15,Fwhich focused on enforcing Parades
OL,16,FCommission conditions of keeping those
OL,17,Ffrom the march from entering Scarva,
OL,18,Fand blocked off several bridges in the
OL,19,Fvillage.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
