PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781021473
OL,3,CMP rejects criticism from 'armchair
OL,4,Cgenerals' over protest attendance
OL,6,FPolice resources made available
OL,7,Fincluded water cannons and armoured
OL,8,FLand Rovers, as well as Tactical
OL,9,FSupport Group officers.
OL,11,FGavin Robinson accused police of
OL,12,F"impeding" the permitted counter-
OL,13,Fprotest by blocking off Scarva bridge,
OL,14,Fadding "that caused difficulty".
OL,16,FMr Robinson also said that police
OL,17,F"have a job of work to do" in terms of
OL,18,Freviewing the evidence they gathered
OL,19,Ffrom Scarva, in terms of whether
OL,20,FParades Commission conditions were
OL,21,Fbroken.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@JO]vD@HOUvD@_O]yD@AOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
