OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781021473
OL,3,CMP rejects criticism from 'armchair
OL,4,Cgenerals' over protest attendance
OL,6,F"Police have told my colleagues that
OL,7,Fthey will be pursuing those issues and
OL,8,Fprosecutions," he added.
OL,10,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "An
OL,11,Fappropriate and proportionate policing
OL,12,Foperation was implemented in Scarva on
OL,13,FSaturday to maintain public safety
OL,14,Fduring a notified parade and protest.
OL,16,F"Evidence gathering was deployed as
OL,17,Fpart of the operation and footage
OL,18,Fcaptured will be reviewed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@NO]rD@[OUxD@AOU
